title: Welcome home! Studio apt, Modern kitchen, Lrg balcony, Plenty storage
posting_body: ['Our spacious studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments are noticeably larger than neighboring apartment communities.', 'With a large air conditioned living room, private deck and ceiling fans, mirrored closet doors and built-in closet organizers in every bedroom, you’ll be living in comfort.', 'This apartment features:', 'Modern Shaker Cabinets', 'Fully-equipped kitchen', 'Under mount sink', 'Ceiling fan', 'Generous storage', 'Private balcony', 'Garden view', 'Convenient on-site laundry', 'Come Visit us!', 'Park Terrace', '860 Quince Avenue', 'Santa Clara, CA 95051', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday-Friday 9 AM to 6 PM', 'Saturday 9 AM –2 PM', 'Sunday-Monday Closed', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: santa clara, hwy 280, lawrence expy, san tomas expy, kaiser, pets, santa clara unified school district, pomeroy elementary, cabrillo middle school, santa clara high school']
